xsmtp (0.5.2.0)
  * Add update.rdf

xsmtp (0.5.0.0)
  * Fix [#508] Few errors with XSMTP extension

xsmtp (0.4.0.0)
  * Fix [#488] Interdire les pièces jointes lors de l'envoi d'un message flash
