xsmtp (0.3.0.0)
  * Major code refactoring.
  * Added a strong validation engine.
  * Fix [#406] No check in the edit box.
  * Fix [#407] The character ':' is prohibited, text truncated
  * Fix [#435] Allow the user to enter upper case characters in the Exempted-Address field
  * Fix [#439] Last character of a string is lost when ':' is entered in a string
  * Fix [#440] The MCA field accept 1;1; but doesn't accept ;1;1
  * Fix [#454] Fields MCA or Distribution-codes still grayed with both empty

xsmtp (0.2.0.0)
  * First working release
